flowchart TD
  A[Local record] --> C{Pending/failed local mutation?}
  B[Remote record] --> C
  C -->|yes| L[Protect local intent; defer overwrite]
  C -->|no| T{Compare updatedAt and deletion state}
  T -->|remote newer| R[Apply remote snapshot]
  T -->|local newer| Q[Keep local and ensure pending action]
  T -->|same logical state| N[No-op / deduplicate]
